## ✅ PHASE 2 — Core Features (COMPLETE)

### Step 2.1 — Repository Management ✅

- [x] List GitHub repos (paginated, infinite scroll)
- [x] Connect → creates webhook + saves to DB + triggers indexing
- [x] Disconnect → removes from DB
- [x] FREE tier: max 5 repos

### Step 2.2 — GitHub Webhook ✅

- [x] Endpoint: `POST /api/webhooks/github`
- [x] Listens for `pull_request` events (opened, synchronize, reopened)
- [x] Fires `pr.review.requested` Inngest event

### Step 2.3 — AI Review Pipeline (Inngest) ✅

- [x] Step 1: Fetch PR metadata + diff + file stats via Octokit
- [x] Step 2: Retrieve RAG context from Pinecone
- [x] Step 3: Generate review via Gemini 2.5 Flash (advanced prompt engineering)
- [x] Step 4: Post review comment on GitHub PR
- [x] Step 5: Save Review + ReviewDetail + FileChange records to DB
- [x] Concurrency limit: 5 simultaneous reviews
- [x] FREE tier review quota: 5 per repo

### Step 2.5 — Advanced Prompt Engineering ✅ (Replaces Phase 8 static analysis)

- [x] [module/ai/lib/prompts.ts](file:///c:/Users/prana/OneDrive/Desktop/codelensai/module/ai/lib/prompts.ts) — system prompt, user prompt builder, diff utilities
- [x] `REVIEW_SYSTEM_PROMPT` — strict 10-rule contract: file:line citations, severity tiers (🔴🟠🟡🔵⚪), risk score 0-100, concrete fixes for every issue
- [x] `buildReviewPrompt()` — compact user prompt with PR metadata + RAG context + annotated diff
- [x] `annotateDiffWithLineNumbers()` — injects line numbers into diff so AI references exact lines
- [x] `compressDiff()` — reduces 4000+ line diffs by trimming context lines (~20% token savings)
- [x] `getTokenBudget()` — dynamic maxOutputTokens scaling: 1500 (small) → 8000 (1500+ lines)
- [x] Temperature 0.2 — focused, deterministic, less hallucination
- [x] `generateWithFallback()` — primary/backup API key failover
- [x] Output format: `## Risk: X/100` → `## Issues` (by severity) → `## Summary`
- [x] Skips clean files, test files, lockfiles, generated code — zero-waste tokens

### Step 2.4 — RAG Pipeline ✅ (Enhanced in Phase 7)

- [x] [module/ai/lib/rag.ts](file:///c:/Users/prana/OneDrive/Desktop/codelensai/module/ai/lib/rag.ts) — embed + index + retrieve (rewritten with function-level chunking)
- [x] Pinecone `codelens` index (3072 dims, Google embeddings)
- [x] Context injected into review prompt
- [x] Hybrid retrieval: semantic similarity + file-path matching
- [x] Score threshold filtering (>0.3) + dynamic topK based on PR size
- [x] Multi-signal RAG query: title + description + changed files + diff key terms
- [x] [module/ai/lib/chunker.ts](file:///c:/Users/prana/OneDrive/Desktop/codelensai/module/ai/lib/chunker.ts) — function-level code chunking (TS/JS/Python/Go/Rust/Java/etc.)
- [x] [module/ai/lib/file-prioritizer.ts](file:///c:/Users/prana/OneDrive/Desktop/codelensai/module/ai/lib/file-prioritizer.ts) — smart file filtering + priority scoring

