## 🔴 PHASE 6 — Ollama Migration (v2.0)

> 📄 Full spec: [diff/02-ollama-migration-plan.md](file:///c:/Users/prana/OneDrive/Desktop/codelensai/diff/02-ollama-migration-plan.md)

**Goal:** Replace Gemini (external API cost) with self-hosted Ollama (free).

### Step 6.1 — Create `module/llm/` Abstraction Layer

- [ ] `provider-interface.ts` — `LLMProvider` + `EmbeddingProvider` interfaces
- [ ] `ollama-provider.ts` — Ollama HTTP client
- [ ] `gemini-provider.ts` — wrap existing gemini.ts as named provider
- [ ] `model-config.ts` — `MODEL_REGISTRY` (code-review: deepseek-coder-v2:16b, etc.)
- [ ] `feature-flags.ts` — `LLM_PROVIDER=ollama|gemini` env switching

### Step 6.2 — Refactor All LLM Integration Points

- [ ] [inngest/functions/review.ts](file:///c:/Users/prana/OneDrive/Desktop/codelensai/inngest/functions/review.ts) → `llmProvider.generate()`
- [ ] [app/api/ai/summarize/route.ts](file:///c:/Users/prana/OneDrive/Desktop/codelensai/app/api/ai/summarize/route.ts) → `llmProvider.generate()`
- [ ] [app/api/ai/generate/route.ts](file:///c:/Users/prana/OneDrive/Desktop/codelensai/app/api/ai/generate/route.ts) → `llmProvider.generate()`
- [ ] [module/ai/lib/rag.ts](file:///c:/Users/prana/OneDrive/Desktop/codelensai/module/ai/lib/rag.ts) → `embeddingProvider.embed()` (768 dims)
- [ ] Create new Pinecone index `codelens-v2` (768 dims for nomic-embed-text)
- [ ] Re-index all repos via `inngest/functions/reindex.ts`

### Step 6.3 — Gradual Rollout

- [ ] Shadow mode: both run in parallel, Gemini served to users
- [ ] Canary: 10% traffic to Ollama
- [ ] Full migration: all to Ollama, keep Gemini keys for rollback

