- [x] [module/ai/lib/rag.ts](file:///c:/Users/prana/OneDrive/Desktop/codelensai/module/ai/lib/rag.ts) — rewritten: function-level chunks, `indexFiles()`, `deleteFileVectors()`, `deleteRepoVectors()`, `buildRetrievalQuery()`, hybrid retrieval, score filtering, dynamic topK
- [x] [inngest/functions/review.ts](file:///c:/Users/prana/OneDrive/Desktop/codelensai/inngest/functions/review.ts) — enhanced RAG query (multi-signal), removed broken auditLog reference
