### UI (Not Yet Done)

- [ ] Show indexing status badge per repo in Settings
- [ ] "Re-index" button per repo (rate limited: 1/hour)

### Key Improvements

| Before | After |
|--------|-------|
| 120-file cap, whole-file embeddings | 500-file smart-prioritized, function-level chunks |
| N recursive API calls per file | 1 Git Trees API call + parallel blob fetches |
| Full re-index only | Incremental delta indexing on PR merge + daily cron sync |
| Weak RAG query (title only) | Multi-signal query (title + desc + files + diff terms) |
| No score filtering | Score threshold >0.3, dynamic topK (4-12) |
| No indexing state tracking | Full `IndexingState` model with status, SHA, counts |

