## ✅ PHASE 8 — Advanced AI Deep Analysis (COMPLETE — replaced static risk engine)

> **Original plan:** Separate `module/risk/` static analysis engine with regex patterns.  
> **What we built instead:** Integrated line-level deep analysis directly into the AI review prompt — smarter, faster, no new models needed.

**Goal:** Every PR review includes file:line-level issue identification, severity classification, concrete fixes, and a 0-100 risk score — all from a single AI call.

### What The AI Now Produces

```
## Risk: 72/100 — SQL injection in auth handler

## Issues
### 🔴 Critical
- **src/auth.ts:42-48** — unsanitized user input in SQL query
  ```ts
  // fix: use parameterized query
  const result = await db.query(sql`SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = ${userId}`)
  ```

### 🟠 Warning  
- **src/utils/parse.ts:15** — unchecked null dereference
  ```ts
  // fix: add null check
  if (!data?.items) return [];
  ```

### 🟡 Suggestion
- **src/api/handler.ts:88-102** — cognitive complexity 18, simplify with early returns

## Summary
2-3 sentences: what changed, quality, key risk.
```

### Implementation ✅

- [x] [module/ai/lib/prompts.ts](file:///c:/Users/prana/OneDrive/Desktop/codelensai/module/ai/lib/prompts.ts) — `REVIEW_SYSTEM_PROMPT` (10-rule contract) + `buildReviewPrompt()` + diff utilities
- [x] Line-number annotation on diffs → AI references exact `file:line` ranges
- [x] Diff compression for large PRs (4000+ lines) → ~20% fewer input tokens
- [x] Dynamic token budget: 1500 tokens (tiny PR) → 8000 tokens (1500+ line PR)
- [x] Temperature 0.2 for focused, consistent output
- [x] Severity tiers: 🔴 Bug > 🟠 Security > 🟡 Performance > 🔵 Quality > ⚪ Style
- [x] Skip clean files entirely — only report problems
- [x] Uses `generateWithFallback()` for API key failover

### Before vs After

| Before (old prompt) | After (advanced prompt engineering) |
|---|---|
| Generic "expert code reviewer" | Strict 10-rule system contract |
| No line references | Every issue cites `file:line` with fix |
| 6 sections (walkthrough, mermaid, etc.) | 3 sections (risk, issues, summary) |
| No token budgeting | Dynamic 1500–8000 based on PR size |
| Temperature ~1.0 | 0.2 — focused, deterministic |
| No severity classification | 5 tiers: 🔴🟠🟡🔵⚪ |
| No risk score | 0-100 risk score on every PR |
| Reviewed clean files with praise | Skips clean files entirely |

